::Hevn::
       He finally catches up to Blackstorm and the others and lands returning 
to his standard winged centaur mode for the time being.  "Blackstorm, Maxima, 
strangers I don't know.  The traitor can be safely presumed dead."  He says 
all of this with a straight face and then looks to the others.  "Now then, I 
believe introductions are in order."

--part1_1c5.9af3a47.2c07a772_boundary
